channel.title: Free stoofs
channel.description:
um found some unfinished business was a 3d map editor (early stage) using jmonkeyengine, feel free to use it to continue on or whatever. has ability to load sectors around the main sector & use space bar to switch between fly camera & tile selector. shouldn't be too hard at all from here to turn it into an editor.
http://uppit.com/9t053u81jry3/World_Builder.zip
edit: id give you guys everything else i had, but i lost all the good stuffs. kryptix was the only other one with the auction house code, and that model editor stuff i had got lost in a format as did a lot of other stuff.
